                             103:        decoded.flush();                                                                                                                                                        
                             104:        return new DecodeResult(parameters);                                                                                                                                    
                             105:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             106:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             107:    // whitespace                                                                                                                                                               
                             108:    //   0  0x00  Null (NUL)                                                                                                                                                    
                             109:    //   9  0x09  Tab (HT)                                                                                                                                                      
                             110:    //  10  0x0A  Line feed (LF)                                                                                                                                                
                             111:    //  12  0x0C  Form feed (FF)                                                                                                                                                
                             112:    //  13  0x0D  Carriage return (CR)                                                                                                                                          
                             113:    //  32  0x20  Space (SP)                                                                                                                                                    
                             114:    private static boolean isWhitespace(int c)                                                                                                                                  
                             115:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             116:        switch (c)                                                                                                                                                              
                             117:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             118:        case 0:                                                                                                                                                                 
                             119:        case 9:                                                                                                                                                                 
                             120:        case 10:                                                                                                                                                                
                             121:        case 12:                                                                                                                                                                
                             122:        case 13:                                                                                                                                                                
                             123:        case 32:                                                                                                                                                                
                             124:            return true;                                                                                                                                                        
                             125:        default:                                                                                                                                                                
                             126:            return false;                                                                                                                                                       
                             127:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             128:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             129:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             130:    private static boolean isEOD(int c)                                                                                                                                         
                             131:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             132:        return c == '>';                                                                                                                                                        
                             133:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             134:                                                                                                                                                                                
                             135:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                   
                             136:    public void encode(InputStream input, OutputStream encoded, COSDictionary parameters)                                                                                       
                             137:        throws IOException                                                                                                                                                      
                             138:    {                                                                                                                                                                           
                             139:        int byteRead;                                                                                                                                                           
                             140:        while ((byteRead = input.read()) != -1)                                                                                                                                 
                             141:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             142:            Hex.writeHexByte((byte)byteRead, encoded);                                                                                                                          
                             143:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             144:        encoded.flush();                                                                                                                                                        
                             145:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             146:}                                                                                                                                                                               
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             </code>                                                                                                                                                                             
                             <code>                                                                                                                                                                              
                             pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/filter/RunLengthDecodeFilter.java:1-190                                                                                                      
                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             1:/*                                                                                                                                                                                
                             2: * Licensed to the Apache Software Foundation (ASF) under one or more                                                                                                             
                             3: * contributor license agreements.  See the NOTICE file distributed with                                                                                                          
                             4: * this work for additional information regarding copyright ownership.                                                                                                            
                             5: * The ASF licenses this file to You under the Apache License, Version 2.0                                                                                                        
                             6: * (the "License"); you may not use this file except in compliance with                                                                                                           
                             7: * the License.  You may obtain a copy of the License at                                                                                                                          
                             8: *                                                                                                                                                                                
                             9: *      http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0                                                                                                                                
                             10: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             11: * Unless required by applicable law or agreed to in writing, software                                                                                                           
                             12: * distributed under the License is distributed on an "AS IS" BASIS,                                                                                                             
                             13: * WITHOUT WARRANTIES OR CONDITIONS OF ANY KIND, either express or implied.                                                                                                      
                             14: * See the License for the specific language governing permissions and                                                                                                           
                             15: * limitations under the License.                                                                                                                                                
                             16: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             17:package org.apache.pdfbox.filter;                                                                                                                                                
                             18:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             19:import java.io.IOException;                                                                                                                                                      
                             20:import java.io.InputStream;                                                                                                                                                      
                             21:import java.io.OutputStream;                                                                                                                                                     
                             22:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             23:import org.apache.pdfbox.cos.COSDictionary;                                                                                                                                      
                             24:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             25:/**                                                                                                                                                                              
                             26: * Decompresses data encoded using a byte-oriented run-length encoding algorithm,                                                                                                
                             27: * reproducing the original text or binary data                                                                                                                                  
                             28: *                                                                                                                                                                               
                             29: * @author Ben Litchfield                                                                                                                                                        
                             30: * @author Tilman Hausherr                                                                                                                                                       
                             31: */                                                                                                                                                                              
                             32:final class RunLengthDecodeFilter extends Filter                                                                                                                                 
                             33:{                                                                                                                                                                                
                             34:    private static final int RUN_LENGTH_EOD = 128;                                                                                                                               
                             35:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             36:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                    
                             37:    public DecodeResult decode(InputStream encoded, OutputStream decoded,                                                                                                        
                             38:                                         COSDictionary parameters, int index) throws IOException                                                                                 
                             39:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             40:        int dupAmount;                                                                                                                                                           
                             41:        byte[] buffer = new byte[128];                                                                                                                                           
                             42:        while ((dupAmount = encoded.read()) != -1 && dupAmount != RUN_LENGTH_EOD)                                                                                                
                             43:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             44:            if (dupAmount <= 127)                                                                                                                                                
                             45:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             46:                int amountToCopy = dupAmount + 1;                                                                                                                                
                             47:                int compressedRead;                                                                                                                                              
                             48:                while (amountToCopy > 0)                                                                                                                                         
                             49:                {                                                                                                                                                                
                             50:                    compressedRead = encoded.read(buffer, 0, amountToCopy);                                                                                                      
                             51:                    // EOF reached?                                                                                                                                              
                             52:                    if (compressedRead == -1)                                                                                                                                    
                             53:                    {                                                                                                                                                            
                             54:                        break;                                                                                                                                                   
                             55:                    }                                                                                                                                                            
                             56:                    decoded.write(buffer, 0, compressedRead);                                                                                                                    
                             57:                    amountToCopy -= compressedRead;                                                                                                                              
                             58:                }                                                                                                                                                                
                             59:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             60:            else                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             62:                int dupByte = encoded.read();                                                                                                                                    
                             63:                // EOF reached?                                                                                                                                                  
                             64:                if (dupByte == -1)                                                                                                                                               
                             65:                {                                                                                                                                                                
                             66:                    break;                                                                                                                                                       
                             67:                }                                                                                                                                                                
                             68:                for (int i = 0; i < 257 - dupAmount; i++)                                                                                                                        
                             69:                {                                                                                                                                                                
                             70:                    decoded.write(dupByte);                                                                                                                                      
                             71:                }                                                                                                                                                                
                             72:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             73:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             74:        return new DecodeResult(parameters);                                                                                                                                     
                             75:    }                                                                                                                                                                            
                             76:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             77:    @Override                                                                                                                                                                    
                             78:    protected void encode(InputStream input, OutputStream encoded, COSDictionary parameters)                                                                                     
                             79:            throws IOException                                                                                                                                                   
                             80:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             81:        // Not used in PDFBox except for testing the decoder.                                                                                                                    
                             82:        int lastVal = -1;                                                                                                                                                        
                             83:        int byt;                                                                                                                                                                 
                             84:        int count = 0;                                                                                                                                                           
                             85:        boolean equality = false;                                                                                                                                                
                             86:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             87:        // buffer for "unequal" runs, size between 2 and 128                                                                                                                     
                             88:        byte[] buf = new byte[128];                                                                                                                                              
                             89:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             90:        while ((byt = input.read()) != -1)                                                                                                                                       
                             91:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             92:            if (lastVal == -1)                                                                                                                                                   
                             93:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             94:                // first time                                                                                                                                                    
                             95:                lastVal = byt;                                                                                                                                                   
                             96:                count = 1;                                                                                                                                                       
                             97:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             98:            else                                                                                                                                                                 
                             99:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             100:                if (count == 128)                                                                                                                                               
                             101:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             102:                    if (equality)                                                                                                                                               
                             103:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             104:                        // max length of equals                                                                                                                                 
                             105:                        encoded.write(129); // = 257 - 128                                                                                                                      
                             106:                        encoded.write(lastVal);                                                                                                                                 
                             107:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             108:                    else                                                                                                                                                        
                             109:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             110:                        // max length of unequals                                                                                                                               
                             111:                        encoded.write(127);                                                                                                                                     
                             112:                        encoded.write(buf, 0, 128);                                                                                                                             
                             113:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             114:                    equality = false;                                                                                                                                           
                             115:                    lastVal = byt;                                                                                                                                              
                             116:                    count = 1;                                                                                                                                                  
                             117:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             118:                else if (count == 1)                                                                                                                                            
                             119:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             120:                    if (byt == lastVal)                                                                                                                                         
                             121:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             122:                        equality = true;                                                                                                                                        
                             123:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             124:                    else                                                                                                                                                        
                             125:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             126:                        buf[0] = (byte) lastVal;                                                                                                                                
                             127:                        buf[1] = (byte) byt;                                                                                                                                    
                             128:                        lastVal = byt;                                                                                                                                          
                             129:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             130:                    count = 2;                                                                                                                                                  
                             131:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             132:                else                                                                                                                                                            
                             133:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             134:                    // 1 < count < 128                                                                                                                                          
                             135:                    if (byt == lastVal)                                                                                                                                         
                             136:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             137:                        if (equality)                                                                                                                                           
                             138:                        {                                                                                                                                                       
                             139:                            ++count;                                                                                                                                            
                             140:                        }                                                                                                                                                       
                             141:                        else                                                                                                                                                    
                             142:                        {                                                                                                                                                       
                             143:                            // write all we got except the last                                                                                                                 
                             144:                            encoded.write(count - 2);                                                                                                                           
                             145:                            encoded.write(buf, 0, count - 1);                                                                                                                   
                             146:                            count = 2;                                                                                                                                          
                             147:                            equality = true;                                                                                                                                    
                             148:                        }                                                                                                                                                       
                             149:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             150:                    else                                                                                                                                                        
                             151:                    {                                                                                                                                                           
                             152:                        if (equality)                                                                                                                                           
                             153:                        {                                                                                                                                                       
                             154:                            // equality ends here                                                                                                                               
                             155:                            encoded.write(257 - count);                                                                                                                         
                             156:                            encoded.write(lastVal);                                                                                                                             
                             157:                            equality = false;                                                                                                                                   
                             158:                            count = 1;                                                                                                                                          
                             159:                        }                                                                                                                                                       
                             160:                        else                                                                                                                                                    
                             161:                        {                                                                                                                                                       
                             162:                            buf[count] = (byte) byt;                                                                                                                            
                             163:                            ++count;                                                                                                                                            
                             164:                        }                                                                                                                                                       
                             165:                        lastVal = byt;                                                                                                                                          
                             166:                    }                                                                                                                                                           
                             167:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             168:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             169:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             170:        if (count > 0)                                                                                                                                                          
                             171:        {                                                                                                                                                                       
                             172:            if (count == 1)                                                                                                                                                     
                             173:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             174:                encoded.write(0);                                                                                                                                               
                             175:                encoded.write(lastVal);                                                                                                                                         
                             176:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             177:            else if (equality)                                                                                                                                                  
                             178:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             179:                encoded.write(257 - count);                                                                                                                                     
                             180:                encoded.write(lastVal);                                                                                                                                         
                             181:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             182:            else                                                                                                                                                                
                             183:            {                                                                                                                                                                   
                             184:                encoded.write(count - 1);                                                                                                                                       
                             185:                encoded.write(buf, 0, count);                                                                                                                                   
                             186:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             187:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             188:        encoded.write(RUN_LENGTH_EOD);                                                                                                                                          
                             189:    }                                                                                                                                                                           
                             190:}                                                                                                                                                                               
                             ```

                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             62:    private boolean fetch() throws IOException                                                                                                                                   
                             63:    {                                                                                                                                                                            
                             64:        currentDataIndex = 0;                                                                                                                                                    
                             65:        if (isEOF || inflater.finished())                                                                                                                                        
                             66:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             67:            isEOF = true;                                                                                                                                                        
                             68:            bytesDecoded = 0;                                                                                                                                                    
                             69:            return false;                                                                                                                                                        
                             70:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             71:        if (inflater.needsInput())                                                                                                                                               
                             72:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             73:            int bytesRead = in.read(buffer);                                                                                                                                     
                             74:            if (bytesRead > -1)                                                                                                                                                  
                             75:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             76:                inflater.setInput(buffer, 0, bytesRead);                                                                                                                         
                             77:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             78:            else                                                                                                                                                                 
                             79:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             80:                isEOF = true;                                                                                                                                                    
                             81:                return false;                                                                                                                                                    
                             82:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             83:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             84:        try                                                                                                                                                                      
                             85:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             86:            // overwrite formerly read bytes                                                                                                                                     
                             87:            if (bytesDecoded > 0)                                                                                                                                                
                             88:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             89:                Arrays.fill(decodedData, 0, bytesDecoded, (byte) 0);                                                                                                             
                             90:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             91:            bytesDecoded = inflater.inflate(decodedData);                                                                                                                        
                             92:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             93:        catch (DataFormatException exception)                                                                                                                                    
                             94:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             95:            isEOF = true;                                                                                                                                                        
                             96:            // check if some bytes could be read at all                                                                                                                          
                             97:            int countZeros = 0;                                                                                                                                                  
                             98:            for (int i = 0; i < decodedData.length; i++)                                                                                                                         
                             99:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             100:                if (decodedData[i] == 0)                                                                                                                                        
                             101:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             102:                    countZeros++;                                                                                                                                               
                             103:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             104:                else                                                                                                                                                            
                             105:                {                                                                                                                                                               
                             106:                    countZeros = 0;                                                                                                                                             
                             107:                }                                                                                                                                                               
                             108:            }                                                                                                                                                                   
                             109:            bytesDecoded = decodedData.length - countZeros;                                                                                                                     
                             110:            // don't throw an exception, use the already read data or an empty stream                                                                                           
                             111:            LOG.warn("FlateFilter: premature end of stream due to a DataFormatException = {}",                                                                                  
                             112:                    exception.getMessage());                                                                                                                                    
                             113:            return bytesDecoded > 0;                                                                                                                                            
                             114:        }                                                                                                                                                                       
                             115:        return true;                                                                                                                                                            
                             ```

                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             71:        while ((firstByte = encoded.read()) != -1)                                                                                                                               
                             72:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             73:            // always after first char                                                                                                                                           
                             74:            while (isWhitespace(firstByte))                                                                                                                                      
                             75:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             76:                firstByte = encoded.read();                                                                                                                                      
                             77:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             78:            if (firstByte == -1 || isEOD(firstByte))                                                                                                                             
                             79:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             80:                break;                                                                                                                                                           
                             81:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             82:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             83:            if (REVERSE_HEX[firstByte] == -1)                                                                                                                                    
                             84:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             85:                LOG.error("Invalid hex, int: {} char: {}", firstByte, (char) firstByte);                                                                                         
                             86:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             87:            value = REVERSE_HEX[firstByte] * 16;                                                                                                                                 
                             88:            secondByte = encoded.read();                                                                                                                                         
                             89:                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             90:            if (secondByte == -1 || isEOD(secondByte))                                                                                                                           
                             91:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             92:                // second value behaves like 0 in case of EOD                                                                                                                    
                             93:                decoded.write(value);                                                                                                                                            
                             94:                break;                                                                                                                                                           
                             95:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             96:            if (REVERSE_HEX[secondByte] == -1)                                                                                                                                   
                             97:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             98:                LOG.error("Invalid hex, int: {} char: {}", secondByte, (char) secondByte);                                                                                       
                             99:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             100:            value += REVERSE_HEX[secondByte];                                                                                                                                   
                             101:            decoded.write(value);                                                                                                                                               
                             102:        }

                             ```                                                                                                                                                                                 
                             42:        while ((dupAmount = encoded.read()) != -1 && dupAmount != RUN_LENGTH_EOD)                                                                                                
                             43:        {                                                                                                                                                                        
                             44:            if (dupAmount <= 127)                                                                                                                                                
                             45:            {                                                                                                                                                                    
                             46:                int amountToCopy = dupAmount + 1;                                                                                                                                
                             47:                int compressedRead;                                                                                                                                              
                             48:                while (amountToCopy > 0)                                                                                                                                         
                             49:                {                                                                                                                                                                
                             50:                    compressedRead = encoded.read(buffer, 0, amountToCopy);                                                                                                      
                             51:                    // EOF reached?                                                                                                                                              
                             52:                    if (compressedRead == -1)                                                                                                                                    
                             53:                    {                                                                                                                                                            
                             54:                        break;                                                                                                                                                   
                             55:                    }                                                                                                                                                            
                             56:                    decoded.write(buffer, 0, compressedRead);                                                                                                                    
                             57:                    amountToCopy -= compressedRead;                                                                                                                              
                             58:                }                                                                                                                                                                
                             59:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             60:            else                                                                                                                                                                 
                             61:            {

                             65:                {                                                                                                                                                                
                             66:                    break;                                                                                                                                                       
                             67:                }                                                                                                                                                                
                             68:                for (int i = 0; i < 257 - dupAmount; i++)                                                                                                                        
                             69:                {                                                                                                                                                                
                             70:                    decoded.write(dupByte);                                                                                                                                      
                             71:                }                                                                                                                                                                
                             72:            }                                                                                                                                                                    
                             73:        }                                                                                                                                                                        
                             ```
